                The numerical strength of the church has increased from the membership of 22 for adult and 
33 for children to over 100 members for the adults and still counting. Since the church 
started, the church has baptised 86 members. The first baptism was 1, the second was 3 and
the last was 9. The number of the children has also increased tremendously to 80.
            </div>
