                The church recorded an unimaginable amount of Gh¢42,000.00 during the first annual 
harvest in 27th November, 2017, the second was Gh¢43,000.00. The last annual harvest 
recorded Gh¢21,000.00 which was due to the outbreak of the Corona Virus which had made 
things difficult for all.
The first offering recorded was Gh¢285.00 and our present offering and tithes ranges from 
Gh¢600.00 to Gh¢1,000.00 which has been tremendous.

            </div>
        </div>


<br>
